					<div class="cb_item_meta"><span class="cb_item_author" id="cb_item_author_edit_893_1749">Abraham Vegh</span><span class="cb_item_date"><a href="/article/10624#comments_1749" title="link to comment 1749">2009-10-22 19:06</a></span> 
